{"tid":784210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打係用緊IE上網?","createTime":"2018-08-18T07:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T07:43:29.000Z","uid":65120,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a871ad1fb690f7e8b8f9d54ff83e48fd335a9a4b","tid":784210,"uid":65120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"久唔久都會見到啲人鬧IE，話用佢上網lag到仆街，甚至有啲仲會講IE既唯一用黎單撈chrome同firefox！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我次次聽到都會覺得好嬲，因為我自己都係一直都用緊IE，用佢上吓網吹吓水聽吓歌睇吓AV，咩事都無，事實就係佢根本就好撚順無撚問題！<br />\n<br />\n所以我今日上黎就係想還IE一個清白，請大家以後唔好再抹黑IE啦好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween，千禧年仲有幾分鐘就到喇，我順便係度預祝各位巴打新年快樂~<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c826b24e86340f89a92e416520890b0048efc246","tid":784210,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"<del>chrome</del> Netscape"},{"pid":"b38109ae548be2fef12cf2a952f30fffec1f8ac7","tid":784210,"uid":185589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:42:13.000Z","msg":"<del>Chrome</del> Firefox"},{"pid":"4a64fb89eeadd64b6ef34304000b328bae43f49f","tid":784210,"uid":172485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"公司廢撚柒尻屌系電腦用chrome會輕機，逼住用IE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過就黎last day<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7726085ea883911063f05faf3142e0b38470635e","tid":784210,"uid":185589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"Chrome有得Custom啲Setting, 個GUI都好睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}